<ptxt>
5,171 ± 51.7 Ω
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Except above
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Measure resistance between the following terminals under each condition in the table.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check for continuity between terminals “2” and “3”.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Set tester at diode range when measuring between terminals “2” and “3”.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
If check result is not satisfactory, replace hands-free switch.
</ptxt>
